   IMPORTANT - TELEPHONE CHANGES  
 ''
 On  Thursday 15th of March  we plan to
move the hardware which runs the system.

We hope and expect the move to take only
a few hours and, therefore, we expect
there to be no loss of normal logon
time. As many of you will know, things
are rarely this simple so there is a
chance we may not be online on time on
Thursday evening.

If you should forget the new phone
numbers, you can ring the old one where
you will find messages telling you what
the new numbers are. Any mail sent to
Perivale will be re-directed to Camden.

As soon as we are connected at the new
address we should be able to release the
first set of Fastrak node numbers.

